history.content:
Want to have your voice heard by the EECS department faculty, staff, and the Chairs?

The EECS Department welcomes you to fill out the 2021-2022 EECS Undergraduate Survey.

The EECS Department and HKN, as well as other student orgs, have created the 2021-2022 EECS Undergraduate Survey to gather student input. This is a great opportunity to voice your questions, concerns, and suggestions to the department, who rely on this survey as a major source of student feedback!

We’ll be having a prize drawing to win one of ten (10) $10 Amazon gift cards! Just be sure to complete the form at the end of the survey. Your response is completely anonymous. We encourage you to respond openly and honestly!
